  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To identify the potential serum biomarkers with regard to the severity of pneumonia, and to
      further evaluate the prognostic value of these markers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      First, we will collect serum samples from patients with pneumonia. Then we will identify
      biomarkers differentially expressed between non-severe pneumonia and severe pneumonia. We
      will further evaluate the prognostic value of these markers for pneumonia.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
